Package mumble.mburger.sdk.MBClient.MBData.MBElements

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MBAddressElement
    Identifies an address with latitude and longitude
    MBCheckboxElement
    Identifies a boolean class
    MBDateElement
    Identifies a date class with some utility methods to format and get milliseconds instead of seconds
    MBDropdownElement
    Identifies a dropdown value, may be linked to a poll or a list
    MBGenericElement
    Identifies a generic element which simply has the content value of the element, it must be parsed and casted by the developer
    MBImages
    Identifies an array of images, it will always be and array even if the image added in the backend is unique
    MBMediaElement
    Identifies an array of files, it will always be and array even if the file added in the backend is unique
    MBPollAnswers
    Identifies an array of answers for a poll.
    MBTextElement
    Identifies a class with text and title
    MBTitleElement
    Identifies a class title
    MBWYSIWYGElement
    Identifies a class with title HTML text
